    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Unfortunately, 2020 has been a year of "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "many riots"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ". The most tragic thing about the violence is the loss of human life, followed by the loss of "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            1
          ],
          1,
          "people’s livelihood"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " or home. But for most, their vehicle is the "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            2
          ],
          1,
          "second most expensive asset they own"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", plus it’s the thing that allows them to get around. Even if a car is a hobby vehicle, having it "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            3
          ],
          1,
          "severely damaged"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " or completely destroyed in a riot is still a nightmare. What’s even worse is to find out after the fact your insurance won’t cover the damage, leaving you high and dry."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      10,
      1
